225
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,800
NAMNUNG: It's not cruel.

226
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:37,520
NAMNUNG: It's just us being clear about our own wants.

227
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:41,000
NAMNUNG: Suppose we lower our standards
to date someone.

228
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,880
NAMNUNG: In the future, we might not be happy.

229
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:44,120
SUNNY: It's true.

230
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,320
SUNNY: The next game is mine.

231
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:46,440
NAMNUNG: Is there a game?

232
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,320
SUNNY: Sure. You prepared some. I prepared some too.

233
00:07:48,320 --> 00:07:49,160
NAMNUNG: What kind of game?

234
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:51,160
SUNNY: The game is "Red Flag or Green Flag".

235
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:53,320
NAMNUNG: Oh, I love this one.

236
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,960
NAMNUNG: Well, let's take turns
asking each other questions.

237
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,800
SUNNY: Okay is green. Not okay is red.

238
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,680
NAMNUNG: Okay.

239
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:02,440
(1. Holding your hands on the first date)
SUNNY: If on the first date, he holds your hand first.

240
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,320
SUNNY: Is it okay? Green or red?

241
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:12,200
NAMNUNG: One, two, three.

242
00:08:12,200 --> 00:08:13,200
(NAMNUNG: Green)
NAMNUNG: Green.

243
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:14,160
(SUNNY: Green) - SUNNY: Okay.
- NAMNUNG: A green.

244
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,560
NAMNUNG: I feel like it's quite normal

245
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,520
NAMNUNG: to hold hands like this.

246
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,520
NAMNUNG: It's cute, you know, all that.

247
00:08:19,520 --> 00:08:21,600
SUNNY: Holding hands is fine, but not anything else.

248
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,320
NAMNUNG: Oh, SUNNY.

249
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,800
NAMNUNG: Next, my question.

250
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,960
(2. The person approaching has a partner already)
NAMNUNG: If that person already has a partner,

251
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:29,920
NAMNUNG: but they're still trying to court us...

252
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:30,800
SUNNY: Do we even need to ask?

253
00:08:31,738 --> 00:08:32,732
NAMNUNG: One, two, three.

254
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:35,560
(NAMNUNG: Red; SUNNY: Red)
NAMNUNG: Red for sure.

255
00:08:35,560 --> 00:08:38,160
SUNNY: If you have a partner, stay with them.

256
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,200
SUNNY: If you have a partner
but want to court others...

257
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,320
- SUNNY: Then become single.
- NAMNUNG: Be single, then.

258
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,360
SUNNY: Well, there's nothing wrong with that.

259
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,760
SUNNY: If you want to court anyone,
even thousands, you can.

260
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,560
NAMNUNG: Up to you.

261
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:50,120
NAMNUNG: But if you have a partner
and want me, then it's a no.

262
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,560
SUNNY: Those who already have a partner

263
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:53,920
SUNNY: court someone new and become their partner.

264
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:56,080
SUNNY: They'll do that to you again
and find someone new.

265
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:58,640
NAMNUNG: Right, we'll be treated the same.
Who wants to be with someone like this?

266
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,920
SUNNY: Okay, are we green or red flag?

267
00:09:00,920 --> 00:09:04,160
(3. Court people because of their looks)
SUNNY: Court someone as they're good-looking.

268
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,400
(NAMNUNG: Green; SUNNY: Green)
NAMNUNG: One, two, three.

269
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:12,960
NAMNUNG: It's normal. We're single.
We can choose whoever we approach.

270
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,440
NAMNUNG: If they're our type, then it's up to us.

271
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:16,280
SUNNY: How can our taste be wrong?

272
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:18,040
NAMNUNG: Yeah, we don't have a partner yet.

273
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:18,920
- NAMNUNG: Isn't that right?
- SUNNY: True.

274
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,480
NAMNUNG: If it's the other question, it's a "TBD."

275
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,360
NAMNUNG: Let's take this one instead.

276
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,560
NAMNUNG: Suppose

277
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:27,720
NAMNUNG: that person is very good-looking... That guy
matches almost every specification with good appearance,

278
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,720
(4. Matches the type but has a bad personality)
NAMNUNG: but his personality isn't good at all.

279
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:30,600
SUNNY: Okay.

280
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:33,440
NAMNUNG: One, two.

281
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,160
(NAMNUNG: Red)
NAMNUNG: Red.

282
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,160
(SUNNY: Yellow)
NAMNUNG: Yellow.

283
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:37,080
- SUNNY: It's yellow because...
- NAMNUNG: There's no...

284
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:39,200
SUNNY: In some perspectives, it might be green.

285
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,560
SUNNY: If he's good-looking
but has a bad personality...

286
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:44,120
SUNNY: We 'eat' him because we like his looks.

287
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:46,640
- SUNNY: But we don't 'eat' his personality.
- NAMNUNG: Eat and go home.

288
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,240
SUNNY: Eat and go back.

289
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:51,320
SUNNY: It depends on what purpose he serves us.

290
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,120
SUNNY: But if it's about being a partner,
maybe not yet.

291
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:55,080
NAMNUNG: I understand, but I feel that...

292
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,600
NAMNUNG: Just thinking about being near someone

293
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:02,320
NAMNUNG: who has a bad personality
or doesn't suit me, then it's a TBD.

294
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:04,440
(5. Arriving late on the first date)
SUNNY: If on the first date,

295
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,280
SUNNY: he arrives late.

296
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,280
SUNNY: Red or green?

297
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:09,440
NAMNUNG: Okay. One, two, three.

298
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:11,320
(NAMNUNG: Yellow; SUNNY: Red)
NAMNUNG: Yellow.

299
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:13,120
NAMNUNG: We don't know

300
00:10:13,120 --> 00:10:14,400
NAMNUNG: if he has experienced something or not.

301
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:16,360
NAMNUNG: We have to listen to him first, but I feel...

302
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:22,400
NAMNUNG: I'm flexible with time.
But if it becomes a habit, then it's a TBD.

303
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:25,320
SUNNY: I feel that I'm not good
with people who arrive late.

304
00:10:26,040 --> 00:10:28,880
SUNNY: Because I'm someone who always arrives early.

305
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:31,400
SUNNY: And if they really want to be with you,
and they want to date you,

306
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,560
SUNNY: why do they make you wait?

307
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:34,680
SUNNY: If I don't want you to wait,
you shouldn't make me wait.

308
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:37,920
SUNNY: If you're late for the first date, won't you be
late for the second, third, fourth, fifth also?

309
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,400
SUNNY: Time is for making a living.

310
00:10:39,400 --> 00:10:40,320
NAMNUNG: Haha.

311
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:42,000
NAMNUNG: Time is valuable. It can earn money.

312
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,520
NAMNUNG: Speaking of the first date.

313
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,680
(6. Expecting to split the bill on the first date)
NAMNUNG: If they expect you to

314
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:47,960
NAMNUNG: split the bill. Is it red or green?

315
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,400
SUNNY: Okay.

316
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,920
- SUNNY: One, two, three.
- NAMNUNG: One, two, three.

317
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:53,760
(SUNNY: Yellow)
NAMNUNG: Yellow.

318
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,680
(NAMNUNG: Green)
NAMNUNG: Green.

319
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:56,880
NAMNUNG: For our food, we pay for our part.

320
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,960
NAMNUNG: They pay for their part.

321
00:10:57,960 --> 00:10:59,400
NAMNUNG: If they're okay with this, it's okay.

322
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:01,560
SUNNY: Personally, I think the one who asks

323
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:03,080
SUNNY: should be the one who pays.

324
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:06,320
- SUNNY: Suppose I go on a date with you. I invite you.
- NAMNUNG: That makes sense.

325
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:10,440
SUNNY: I have to pay. Why should
the person who was invited pay?

326
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:14,120
SUNNY: If you invite and expect them to split the bill,
no, you wanted me more.

327
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:17,440
SUNNY: You obviously wanna me more.
You call me, so you have to pay.

328
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:19,440
NAMNUNG: Understood. This is understandable.

329
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:22,440
SUNNY: The second time, I agree to see you again.

330
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:25,280
SUNNY: It means I like you enough
from the first round to the second.

331
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:25,920
NAMNUNG: Okay.

332
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:28,360
SUNNY: Okay, maybe I concern fifty-fifty.

333
00:11:28,474 --> 00:11:29,960
NAMNUNG: Make sense. Okay.

334
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,440
NAMNUNG: The question wasn't clear.
My apologies, SUNNY.

335
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,440
SUNNY: Thank you for apologizing.

336
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,520
NAMNUNG: We've wrapped up
the Red Flag or Green Flag game.

337
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,400
NAMNUNG: Let's have a conversation instead.

338
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,040
NAMNUNG: But let's not make it
an ordinary conversation.

339
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:41,960
NAMNUNG: We'll have a lie detection.

340
00:11:41,960 --> 00:11:44,080
NAMNUNG: Suppose I ask you a question, SUNNY,

341
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,120
NAMNUNG: and you answer me.

342
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,144
NAMNUNG: But if I feel...

343
00:11:46,208 --> 00:11:46,920
SUNNY: I'm not buying it.

344
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,640
NAMNUNG: I'm not buying it.

345
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,160
NAMNUNG: You better start explaining.

346
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:49,920
SUNNY: Sure.

347
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,520
NAMNUNG: To make me... "Ah, okay, believe it."

348
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,720
- NAMNUNG: Got it?
- SUNNY: Catch each other out.

349
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,440
NAMNUNG: Let's start with the first question.

350
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,320
NAMNUNG: When someone says they're late for a date,

351
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,440
NAMNUNG: but they look great, exactly our type.

352
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,560
NAMNUNG: You really like them. Can you wait for him?

353
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,440
NAMNUNG: Let's assume you're the one inviting them.

354
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,840
- SUNNY: 15 minutes.
- NAMNUNG: 15 minutes.

355
00:12:04,840 --> 00:12:05,760
NAMNUNG: This is believable.

356
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:09,680
NAMNUNG: Because SUNNY is
someone who is very punctual and arrives early.

357
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,160
NAMNUNG: But for SUNNY, 15 minutes is...

358
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:13,160
SUNNY: It feels very long.

359
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:15,240
SUNNY: No matter how beautiful
or handsome they are, oh, wow.

360
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:18,440
- SUNNY: Making me wait this long, they might
not respect me. - NAMNUNG: The percentage...

361
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:20,720
NAMNUNG: The percentage of liking
might decrease, right?

362
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,520
NAMNUNG: Any questions?

363
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,680
SUNNY: Let's start with the same question.

364
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:24,320
NAMNUNG: Let's take it from the times I've waited.

365
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:27,440
NAMNUNG: He had work,
and then drove an hour in heavy traffic.

366
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:30,240
SUNNY: Huh! So he really looks great, right?

367
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:34,160
NAMNUNG: Asking how good-looking he is,
I'm the one inviting him to go out.

368
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:37,720
NAMNUNG: I can understand.
Bangkok traffic jams are understandable.

369
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,000
NAMNUNG: I keep waiting,
never thinking about going home.

370
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,560
NAMNUNG: Because he'll come anyway, but...

371
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:43,000
NAMNUNG: After that date, I feel like

372
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,680
NAMNUNG: he's not that committed to me.

373
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:45,960
SUNNY: Absolutely.

374
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:47,120
SUNNY: Bangkok traffic jams every day.

375
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,680
SUNNY: Don't pretend you don't know
Bangkok traffic jams every day.

376
00:12:49,680 --> 00:12:53,080
SUNNY: You already know
how long it takes from work to here.

377
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:56,080
SUNNY: If you can't make it by 7 PM,
then schedule it for 8 PM.

378
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:58,200
SUNNY: Don't schedule for 7 PM
when you know there's traffic.

379
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,600
SUNNY: It just makes no sense.

380
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:00,720
NAMNUNG: Do you believe it?

381
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,920
SUNNY: I believe it. I do.

382
00:13:02,432 --> 00:13:04,080
NAMNUNG: I'm a very chill person.

383
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,880
NAMNUNG: Really.

384
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:07,240
SUNNY: So, if you meet someone for the first time,

385
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,640
SUNNY: would you actually dare
to ask for their socials?

386
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:10,880
SUNNY: They're very good looking, perfectly your type.

387
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:14,880
SUNNY: Or do you have to giggle near them first?

388
00:13:14,880 --> 00:13:15,960
NAMNUNG: Probably like...

389
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:20,080
- SUNNY: Have to giggle.
- NAMNUNG: Have to look first.

390
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,960
NAMNUNG: Are they here yet? Are they here?

391
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:25,600
NAMNUNG: Is it possible?
It's possible to ask but rarely.

392
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:27,040
NAMNUNG: Has to be exactly my type, like...

393
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,320
NAMNUNG: Want it.

394
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:33,240
SUNNY: Suppose you're standing in some lobby.

395
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,760
SUNNY: They're about to get into the car.

396
00:13:34,760 --> 00:13:37,880
SUNNY: You only have 1 or 2 minutes.
Do you dare to do it?

397
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:38,560
NAMNUNG: No.

398
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:39,600
SUNNY: Oh, okay, miss out then.

399
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,480
NAMNUNG: In my perspective, it feels like

400
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,920
NAMNUNG: a good looking person

401
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:47,160
NAMNUNG: passing by in a glance and soon forgotten.

402
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:49,240
NAMNUNG: Tomorrow you'll forget how they look.

403
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:51,360
SUNNY: But they're really exactly your type.

404
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:53,440
NAMNUNG: Sometimes, I just walk past them and then...

405
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,720
NAMNUNG: Ugh, I should've just asked.

406
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:58,920
NAMNUNG: It happens, but it's just a fleeting feeling.

407
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:00,720
NAMNUNG: Do you believe it?

408
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,440
SUNNY: Yes.

409
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,600
NAMNUNG: Okay.

410
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:03,760
NAMNUNG: And you?

411
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,760
SUNNY: If it's me, I'll ask.

412
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,160
- NAMNUNG: Really?
- SUNNY: I'll ask anyway.

413
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,200
NAMNUNG: Really? You're shy.

414
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:10,760
- SUNNY: When I want something, I want it a lot.
- NAMNUNG: Oh, really?

415
00:14:10,760 --> 00:14:12,720
SUNNY: And it has to be something I really want.

416
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:15,000
- SUNNY: A rare item. Something highly desired.
- NAMNUNG: How do you ask for it?

417
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,440
NAMNUNG: How do you ask for it?

418
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:19,640
SUNNY: I don't usually go out alone
I might be with friends, and then...

419
00:14:21,160 --> 00:14:21,880
NAMNUNG: Let them ask for you.

420
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:22,800
SUNNY: Ask for me.

421
00:14:22,800 --> 00:14:24,040
SUNNY: Please.

422
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:26,640
SUNNY: Could you give them my IG?

423
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:28,720
NAMNUNG: But from the perspective
of the person being asked...

424
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,480
NAMNUNG: Suppose someone asks for my IG,

425
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:33,000
NAMNUNG: but their friend comes to ask, I'd say 'No'.

426
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,960
- SUNNY: Why?
- NAMNUNG: Bring them here now. Ask me themselves.

427
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:38,400
NAMNUNG: If you really like me that much,
ask me yourself.

428
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,000
NAMNUNG: Understand?

429
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,800
NAMNUNG: Have you ever been asked?
It's a feeling like that, you know.

430
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:41,760
NAMNUNG: What do they look like?

431
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,640
NAMNUNG: Should I give it?

432
00:14:42,640 --> 00:14:43,720
NAMNUNG: Or just give it first.

433
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:45,440
NAMNUNG: And then when they message, just...

434
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:47,200
- NAMNUNG: Block them.
- SUNNY: Yeah.

435
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:50,760
SUNNY: Sometimes you see
someone attractive, that's your type.

436
00:14:50,760 --> 00:14:53,200
SUNNY: But they're about a kilometer away.

437
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,520
SUNNY: Okay, maybe half a kilometer away.

438
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:58,040
SUNNY: From this distance, they look attractive.

439
00:14:58,040 --> 00:15:00,000
SUNNY: But I don't dare ask, so my friend goes instead.

440
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,440
SUNNY: Then I just sit there scrolling.

441
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:02,760
SUNNY: It's a TBD.

442
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:03,880
NAMNUNG: Ah, it's a TBD.

443
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,600
SUNNY: Luckily, I didn't ask myself.

444
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:07,960
NAMNUNG: Nah, you may pretend to walk by them.

